parameters: Clea: Should we guard outside the room?

Prince Rex: Inside, there is the guild leader... I want Clea
to come.

Clea: In such an important place...! I think there are more
suitable people than me.

Guild Leader Agonia: Stolge and Celis are out for
negotiations. Shimosu is out of the question... Besides,
there is an important factor.

Prince Rex: It is important that the Dragon Slayer, who has
been recognized by Queen Caron, is present with me in the
negotiation.
Clea: Understood, I will accompany you.

Priestess Sophia: Please leave the security here to us. I
will definitely protect it together with them.

Mage Relm: The Magic Academy is neutral... but well, if it
has come to this, I'll give it my all!
Thief Nora: I'm a thief, so I'll be fine with anything!

Clea: Sophia-san, please don't worry. I will definitely not
let anything happen to Prince Rex.
Priestess Sophia: Yes, I trust Clea-chan, so it'll be fine.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Prince Rex: We've come this far... I can't go back to the
way things were with my uncle.

Prince Rex: Even though I've prepared myself, I still feel
nervous.

Priestess Sophia: Are you going to stop today? It seems like
you're thinking about some important negotiations...

Prince Rex: If it can't be avoided, let's do it today.
Depending on the situation, there might be a possibility of
a battle.
Prince Rex: Please let me know when you're ready.

Royal Court Official Emoni: P-Please wait!

Guild Leader Agonia: What is it? I have no personal business
to discuss with you.

Adventurer's Guild?
Guild Leader Agonia: Who are you?

Guild Leader Agonia: Because I cannot answer this question
immediately. You judge value based on appearances rather
than substance.

Guild Leader Agonia: Let's meet on the battlefield. At that
time, it will be as members of the shadow division, not as
civil servants.
Guild Leader Agonia: Clea, please go to Myukos.
Clea: Understood. What should I do in Myukos?

Guild Leader Agonia: Please join Celis and head to the
Myukos region. Negotiations are expected to be difficult in
that particular area.

Guild Leader Agonia: It may be troublesome, but if you want
to gather information, it's best to go meet that man.
Lex: Understood, I will first go meet Cors-san.

Guild Leader Agonia (Was Prince Lex's statement... really
just a threat?)

Guild Leader Agonia (He seems to be preparing to become

Guild Leader Agonia (Although it seemed that he had
